➜干货贴|伦敦大学学院（UCL）商科类专业介绍（二）
http://www.sohu.com/a/119295637_101368	8755
<p><strong>前天小编为大家整理了UCL 的4个商科专业， 下面为大家介绍剩下的4个。 </strong></p>
<p><strong>Msc Engineering with Finance</strong></p>
<p>这个项目旨在给本科阶段学习工程,管理学等专业的学生一些管理与金融方面的知识与技能来对工程项目的商业维度和金融维度进行深入探究.这个专业的课程教授Professor Mark Miodownik表明,伦敦大学学院UCL是世界上做交叉型研究的最高端院校之一,我们会提供高质量的学术研讨会,技术训练以及充实的研究材料,而最重要的是启发与支持.</p>
<p>Course Provided</p>
<p>Core Modules</p>
<p>Materials and Fatigue</p>
<p>Project Management</p>
<p>Financial Institutions and Markets</p>
<p>New and Renewable Energy Systems</p>
<p>Numerical Analysis for Finance</p>
<p>Options Modules</p>
<p>Advanced Computer Applications in Engineering</p>
<p>Vibration, Acoustics and Control</p>
<p>Compliance, Risk and Regulation</p>
<p>Entrepreneurial Finance</p>
<p>Entry Requirement 录取要求</p>
<p>A minimum of an upper second-class Bachelor's degree from a UK university in engineering, physics or applied mathematics, or an overseas qualification of an equivalent standard.</p>
<p>此专业适合以下专业方向学生申请: 工程,物理科学,应用数学等相关专业.</p>
<p>The English language level for this programme is:Standard</p>
<p>Standard在UCL的语言要求中意味着学生需要有6.5分的雅思,单项不低于6.</p>
<p><strong>Msc Computational finance</strong></p>
<p>这个项目旨在培养学生掌握金融领域中的高级计算方法;如今具备高级计算分析,模型设计与实施的高端人才也一直是银行,基金经理,保险公司,对冲基金,金融软件与数据挖掘等追求的对象. 简单举例,市场上的保险,基金,理财产品在推行前是要进行产品的创造与模拟检测.</p>
<p>Course Provided</p>
<p>Core Modules</p>
<p>Programming and Mathematical Methods for Machine Learning or Introductory Programming, depending on entry qualification</p>
<p>Stochastic Processes for Finance</p>
<p>Financial Data and Statistics</p>
<p>Financial Market Modelling and Analysis</p>
<p>Options Modules</p>
<p>Algorithmics</p>
<p>Applied Computational Finance</p>
<p>Database Systems</p>
<p>Financial Institutions and Markets</p>
<p>Forecasting</p>
<p>Market Risk Measures and Portfolio Theory</p>
<p>Networks and Systemic Risk</p>
<p>Numerical Analysis for Finance</p>
<p>Operational Risk Measurement for Financial Institutions</p>
<p>Programming and Mathematical Methods for Machine Learning</p>
<p>Quantitative and Computational Finance</p>
<p>Software Engineering</p>
<p>Entry Requirement 录取要求</p>
<p>An upper-second class UK Bachelor's degree (or equivalent overseas qualification) in computer science, mathematics, statistics, physics, engineering or a similarly quantitative subject. Programming experience is an advantage but is not mandatory. Relevant work experience is also taken into account.</p>
<p>此专业适合以下专业方向学生申请:计算机科学,数学,统计,物理,工程或计算科学类专业申请.编程等相关的经历将会是优势,但是非强制要求.相关的工作经验也可成为参考依据.</p>
<p>The English language level for this programme is:Good</p>
<p>Good 在UCL的语言要求中意味着学生需要有7分的雅思,单项不低于6.5.</p>
<p><strong>Msc Financial Systems Engineering</strong></p>
<p>这个项目旨在培养追求以软件工程师为职业目标的学生.一些金融服务公司会需要一类人才进行软件工程研发工作,这个项目会让学生在金融计算方向深入学习软件系统工程.</p>
<p>Course Provided</p>
<p>Core Modules</p>
<p>Requirements Engineering and Software Architecture</p>
<p>Software Abstractions and Systems Integration</p>
<p>Validation and Verification</p>
<p>Tools and Environments</p>
<p>Financial Institutions and Markets</p>
<p>Professional Practice</p>
<p>Financial Information Systems</p>
<p>Option Modules</p>
<p>Compliance, Risk and Regulation</p>
<p>People and Security</p>
<p>Networked Systems</p>
<p>Distributed Systems and Security</p>
<p>Entry Requirement 录取要求</p>
<p>A minimum of an upper second-class UK Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or in a science or engineering subject with significant computer science content, or an overseas qualification of an equivalent standard. Relevant work experience may also be taken into account.</p>
<p>此专业适合以下专业项目学生申请:计算机科学或者理工科学类并且以大量计算机科学课程体系的学生申请,相关的工作经验也会成为参考依据.</p>
<p>The English language level for this programme is: Good</p>
<p>Good 在UCL的语言要求中意味着学生需要有7分的雅思,单项不低于6.5。</p>
<p><strong>Msc Financial Risk Management</strong></p>
<p>这个项目旨在培养未来从事风险控制方向的专业人才,来满足当下对量化风险管理专业人才的需求.学生通过这个项目可以充分调动自己的兴趣领域,研究不同方向下的风险控制问题.</p>
<p>Course Provided</p>
<p>Core Modules</p>
<p>Compliance Risk and Regulation</p>
<p>Financial Data and Statistics</p>
<p>Market Risk, Measures and Portfolio Theory</p>
<p>Quantitative and Computational Finance</p>
<p>Option Modules</p>
<p>Applied Computational Finance</p>
<p>Asset Pricing in Continuous Time</p>
<p>Equities, Foreign Exchange and Commodities Modelling</p>
<p>Financial Institutions and Markets</p>
<p>Forecasting</p>
<p>Networks and Systemic Risk</p>
<p>Numerical Analysis for Finance</p>
<p>Operational Risk Measurement for Financial Institutions</p>
<p>Quantitative Modelling of Operational Risk and Insurance Analytics</p>
<p>Stochastic Methods in Finance</p>
<p>Entry Requirement 录取要求</p>
<p>A minimum of an upper second class UK Bachelor's degree, in a relevant discipline, or an overseas qualification of an equivalent standard, with a strong quantitative component evidenced by good performance (higher than 60%) in relevant mathematics, statistics or computation options.</p>
<p>此专业适合以下专业学生申请: 相关专业即可,但是学生需要具备较强的数理分析能力,在数学,统计,计算科学相关课程需要均分达到良好以上(80/85以上水平.)</p>
<p>The English language level for this programme is: Good</p>
<p>Good 在UCL的语言要求中意味着学生需要有7分的雅思,单项不低于6.5。</p>